<h1 class='property-title'>font-variant</h1>
<p class='property-description'>The<code> font-variant </code>CSS property selects a<code> normal</code>, or<code> small-caps </code>face from a font family. Setting<code> font-variant </code>is also possible by using the <code><a rel="custom" href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en/CSS/font">font</a></code>
 shorthand.</p>